{"type":null,"faqId":21633,"title":"为什么手环的蓝牙断开以后，不能自动连接手机蓝牙？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.008333334in;margin-left:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>如果手环和手机距离过远，手环和手机的蓝牙拉距断开，在3分钟内，如果手环重新回到手机蓝牙覆盖范围内，此时手机和手环的蓝牙都处于开启状态，那么手环会自动和手机进行蓝牙连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果手环和手机蓝牙断开3分钟以上，为减少功耗，手环会自动关闭蓝牙，手环界面的蓝牙图标会小时。这时候，如果用户重新进入手机蓝牙覆盖区域，需要按下手环的功能按键，唤醒手环蓝牙，这时候，手环会和之前配对的蓝牙手机主动重新连接。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":209,"faqType":"连接与配对","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5334","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Connection-Paring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1427334705000,"seriesProductName":"B1-Honor","visitedTimes":280,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}